desc: Distressed and destroyed Flannels and Levi denim jeans and pearls look great with womens ruffles and lace in shabby chic clothing for Southern Gypsy, sweet Magnolia style. The perfect mix of eco-friendly "junk" fabrics (lace and doilies) handcrafted and made in Texas in the Good 'Ol USA. Boho-chic meets Western Hippie
